  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 21,
   "id": "f6ef0693-3761-4e4f-b7a4-29279f0108f6",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "#group by Topic and Sentiment\n",
    "topic_wise_sentiment= train.groupby([\"Topic\",\"Sentiment\"]).size().reset_index(name='Count')\n",
    "\n",
    "#Select top 5 topics\n",
    "topic_counts = train['Topic'].value_counts().nlargest(5).index\n",
    "top_topics_sentiments = topic_wise_sentiment[topic_wise_sentiment['Topic'].isin(topic_counts)]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 22,
   "id": "c4bbc03d-eda7-44c2-9707-dec217b6a5ca",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 1200x800 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "plt.figure(figsize=(12,8))\n",
    "sns.barplot(data=top_topics_sentiments[top_topics_sentiments['Sentiment']=='Negative'], x='Topic', y='Count',hue='Topic', palette='viridis', legend=False)\n",
    "plt.title('Top 5 Topics with Negative Sentiments')\n",
    "plt.xlabel('Topic')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('Count')\n",
    "plt.xticks(rotation=45)\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
